            <note xml:id="foot.f4">CD refers to Elizabeth Darwin, Edmund and Emily Caroline Langton, Sophia and <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_6822.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Sophia Henrietta Sulivan</ref>, and <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_6890.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Catherine Sabine Trench</ref>. Elizabeth went to Bournemouth on 25 January 1872 (<ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1218.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Emma Darwin’s</ref> diary (DAR 242)).</note>
